headline: Marshalls to Launch "The Upgrade Lounge" at JFK Airport -- Providing Premium Perks for Every Traveler
summary: Marshalls (NYSE: TJX) is elevating travel just in time for Memorial Day weekend with the debut of The Upgrade Lounge. Open to travelers from May 21–28, this immersive pop-up lounge delivers a premium airport experience—no first-class ticket required. Rooted in the belief that everyone deserves access to better—better quality, better experiences, and better value—Marshalls is bringing its mission beyond the store aisles and into the airport.
